► Main Features


• Flip and shake action to dismiss/postpone alarm;

• Turn off/postpone the alarm with the power button or volume buttons;

• Swipe to delete an alarm;

• Light, dark or system theme;

• Customizable screensaver;

• Material design and dynamic colors;

• … and much more!


► Important information


To ensure that the application works properly, some of your device settings must be changed:


• DO NOT DISTURB: allows the alarm to trigger if notification sounds are muted;


• BATTERY OPTIMIZATION: allows the alarm to trigger if the screen is turned off;


• NOTIFICATIONS: allows the alarm, timer and stopwatch to send a notification when the application is minimized. It also enables the alarm to trigger.


• FULL SCREEN NOTIFICATIONS: for Android 14 only, allows the alarm to trigger if the screen is turned off;


You can change these settings in the following dialogs.


Depending on the Android version of your device, some of these settings are already optimized (e.g. notifications).
